java.lang.Object
org.checkerframework.framework.type.AnnotatedTypeFactory
org.checkerframework.framework.type.GenericAnnotatedTypeFactory<org.checkerframework.framework.flow.CFValue,org.checkerframework.framework.flow.CFStore,org.checkerframework.framework.flow.CFTransfer,org.checkerframework.framework.flow.CFAnalysis>

All Implemented Interfaces:
org.checkerframework.javacutil.AnnotationProvider
public class FormatterAnnotatedTypeFactory extends org.checkerframework.common.basetype.BaseAnnotatedTypeFactory
Adds Format to the type of tree, if it is a String or char literal that represents a satisfiable format. The annotation's value is set to be a list of appropriate ConversionCategory values for every parameter of the format.
